Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: cronwrap3
Version: 1.0.2
Summary: A Python3 cron job wrapper that wraps jobs and enables better error reporting and command timeouts.
Home-page: https://github.com/sharpertool/cronwrap3
Author: Ed Henderson
Author-email: ed@sharpertool.com
